#Depression #poetry 

The battle against depression never ends
I mostly hide it from my friends
Sharing bits and pieces of what troubles me
The real pain I never let them see
Fear keeps bound in chains
All the while the overlord and mental health cause more pain

rawContent:
My #ChronicPain is mostly gone.
My head is clear.
My thoughts are positive.
My executive function is working.
My body is moving.
I feel good.
I feel happy.
I feel hope.

It won't last forever, but I'm enjoying it for now.

#LongCovid #ChronicIllness #MECFS #Depression
